{"tid":2297741,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"想搵番一套電影","createTime":"2020-11-23T13:21:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T23:37:16.000Z","uid":250812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e162ed38b30e67008dd33d31517152c1f3a494aa","tid":2297741,"uid":250812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T13:21:08.000Z","msg":"好耐好耐以前明珠台播過<br />\n記憶好隱約 應該係恐怖片/懸疑<br />\n大概係講有個山洞定唔知乜 住左一班痴線佬<br />\n然後主角唔知要入去做乜<br />\n<br />\n唔記得主角係邊個 淨係記得一個配角<br />\n係一個印地安人 好記得佢為左救主角 引走左一班衰人走  最後不敵人群戰術<br />\n比佢地捉左番去 挷住 係咁用矛吉佢 虐殺佢<br />\n然後下一幕就見佢比啲衰人拋去森林到<br />\n臨死之前見到佢既圖騰動物<br />\n<br />\n就係咁 其他完全唔記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />淨係記得依幕"},{"pid":"a56b6f17717b8f0374a5299947c7af0add9b1141","tid":2297741,"uid":132810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T13:24:04.000Z","msg":"就咁聽都覺恐怖"},{"pid":"ba9dce9fd67ac0ce48e94cec9a0c57cd9efe7cf1","tid":2297741,"uid":1773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T13:26:30.000Z","msg":"apocalypto <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f38b4732c01b08b1812e77d3edaf0814c793ba1e","tid":2297741,"uid":250812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba9dce9fd67ac0ce48e94cec9a0c57cd9efe7cf1","tid":2297741,"uid":1773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T13:26:30.000Z","msg":"apocalypto <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T13:37:28.000Z","msg":"應該唔係 好似成套得果個朋友係印地安人"},{"pid":"b28f9f779ed649547c61ee64cac091d4ef836290","tid":2297741,"uid":250812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a56b6f17717b8f0374a5299947c7af0add9b1141","tid":2297741,"uid":132810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T13:24:04.000Z","msg":"就咁聽都覺恐怖"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T13:38:12.000Z","msg":"對果個好慘既印地安人好深刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/f